/* 首页 = 全屏沉浸界面：立绘铺底 + 暗场压暗 + 所有操作毛玻璃半透明浮层（游戏式单界面） */
.page {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  padding: calc(env(safe-area-inset-top) + 72rpx) 48rpx calc(env(safe-area-inset-bottom) + 44rpx);
  overflow: hidden;
  /* 全背景基底：暖墨黑渐变（立绘叠其上；无立绘的老用户态也有沉浸底） */
  background: linear-gradient(165deg, #36303a 0%, #20232e 58%, #15171f 100%);
}

/* 全屏立绘（固定，不随内容滚） */
.bg-lihe { position: fixed; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: 0; }
/* 暗场：上压一点（标题可读）+ 下压重（按钮/气泡可读） */
.bg-scrim {
  position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 1;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
    rgba(16,18,26,0.50) 0%, rgba(16,18,26,0.04) 26%,
    rgba(16,18,26,0.30) 62%, rgba(16,18,26,0.86) 100%);
}

/* 内容浮在最上层 */
.hero, .grow, .float, .actions, .loading { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

.brand { font-size: 26rpx; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); letter-spacing: 8rpx; margin-bottom: 10rpx; }
.tagline { font-size: 30rpx; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92); letter-spacing: 1rpx; margin-bottom: 22rpx; text-shadow: 0 2rpx 14rpx rgba(0,0,0,0.45); }
.headline {
  font-size: 56rpx; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1.4;
  text-shadow: 0 2rpx 14rpx rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
}

.grow { flex: 1; min-height: 40rpx; }

/* 示例助理：名牌 + 招呼气泡（毛玻璃） */
.float { margin-bottom: 30rpx; }
.float-id { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10rpx; margin-bottom: 14rpx; }
.float-name { font-size: 28rpx; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; text-shadow: 0 1rpx 8rpx rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
.dot { width: 12rpx; height: 12rpx; border-radius: 50%; background: #34d399; animation: presencePulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
@keyframes presencePulse { 0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(52,211,153,0.5); } 50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 8rpx rgba(52,211,153,0); } }
.float-on { font-size: 22rpx; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); text-shadow: 0 1rpx 8rpx rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
.float-bubble {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(24rpx); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24rpx);
  border: 1rpx solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
  color: #fff; font-size: 27rpx; line-height: 1.6;
  padding: 22rpx 26rpx; border-radius: 24rpx; border-bottom-left-radius: 8rpx;
}
.float-note { margin-top: 14rpx; font-size: 22rpx; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-shadow: 0 1rpx 6rpx rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
.caret {
  display: inline-block; width: 3rpx; height: 28rpx; background: var(--accent);
  margin-left: 4rpx; vertical-align: -4rpx; animation: caretBlink 1s step-end infinite;
}
@keyframes caretBlink { 0%,100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0; } }

/* 操作区：全毛玻璃半透明 */
.actions { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20rpx; }
.glass-btn {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
  backdrop-filter: blur(24rpx); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24rpx);
  border: 1rpx solid rgba(255,255,255,0.26);
  color: #fff;
  border-radius: 100rpx;
  padding: 26rpx 0; text-align: center;
  font-size: 30rpx; font-weight: 500;
}
/* 主操作：碧绿半透明，略跳但仍守"半透明/点睛" */
.glass-btn.primary {
  background: rgba(24, 182, 144,0.34);
  border-color: rgba(24, 182, 144,0.6);
}

.loading { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); text-align: center; margin-top: 60rpx; }

/* 收件箱待办角标：碧绿小徽章浮在按钮右上角（主人召回钩子） */
.inbox-btn { position: relative; }
.todo-badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: -12rpx;
  right: 28rpx;
  min-width: 38rpx;
  height: 38rpx;
  padding: 0 12rpx;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  border-radius: 100rpx;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 24rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 38rpx;
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: 0 4rpx 12rpx rgba(24, 182, 144, 0.45);
}
